[section#ifstream.cons
    [:en] [`basic_ifstream] constructors
    [:zh_CN] [`basic_ifstream] 构造函数
]

[%@library basic_ifstream[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
basic_ifstream();
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs an object of class [`basic_ifstream<charT, traits>],
initializing the base class with [`basic_istream(&sb)] and initializing [`sb]
with [`basic_filebuf<charT, traits>())] ([#istream.cons], [#filebuf.cons]).
[:zh_CN] 构造类 [`basic_ifstream<charT, traits>] 的对象，以
[`basic_istream(&sb)] 初始化其基类，并以 [`basic_filebuf<charT, traits>())]
初始化 [`sb]（[#istream.cons]，[#filebuf.cons]）。
[exit:description]

[%@library basic_ifstream[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
explicit basic_ifstream(const char* s,
                        ios_base::openmode mode = ios_base::in);
explicit basic_ifstream(const filesystem::path::value_type* s,
                        ios_base::openmode mode = ios_base::in);  // [:en] wide systems only; see [#fstream.syn]
                                                                  // [|:zh_CN] 仅宽字符系统；参见 [#fstream.syn]
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs an object of class [`basic_ifstream], initializing the base
class with [`basic_istream(&sb)] and initializing [`sb] with
[`basic_filebuf<charT, traits>())] ([#istream.cons], [#filebuf.cons]), then
calls [`rdbuf()->open(s, mode | ios_base::in)].
[:zh_CN] 构造类 [`basic_ifstream] 的对象，以 [`basic_istream(&sb)] 初始化其基类，
并以 [`basic_filebuf<charT, traits>())] 初始化 [`sb]（[#istream.cons]，
[#filebuf.cons]），然后调用 [`rdbuf()->open(s, mode | ios_base::in)]。

[:en] If that function returns a null pointer, calls [`setstate(failbit)].
[:zh_CN] 如果该函数返回空指针，则调用 [`setstate(failbit)]。
[exit:description]

[%@library basic_ifstream[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
explicit basic_ifstream(const string& s,
                        ios_base::openmode mode = ios_base::in);
explicit basic_ifstream(const filesystem::path& s,
                        ios_base::openmode mode = ios_base::in);
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] The same as [`basic_ifstream(s.c_str(), mode)].
[:zh_CN] 与 [`basic_ifstream(s.c_str(), mode)] 相同。
[exit:description]

[%@library basic_ifstream[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
basic_ifstream(basic_ifstream&& rhs);
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Move constructs from the rvalue [`rhs].
[:zh_CN] 从右值 [`rhs] 进行移动构造。

[:en] This is accomplished by move constructing the base class, and the
contained [`basic_filebuf].
[:zh_CN] 这是通过移动构造其基类和其所包含的 [`basic_filebuf] 来达成的。

[:en] Next [`basic_istream<charT, traits>::set_rdbuf(&sb)] is called to install
the contained [`basic_filebuf].
[:zh_CN] 然后调用 [`basic_istream<charT, traits>::set_rdbuf(&sb)] 来安装其所
包含的 [`basic_filebuf]。
[exit:description]
